name: Primal Kingdom by Dayne Henry Jr

metadata.name: The Crowned Predator
metadata.description:
The Panther in this artwork is not just any predator, it's the crowned king of the jungle. The Panther's piercing eyes and confident stance make it clear that it's not to be messed with. 

Additionally, all Primal King NFT holders will be whitelisted for a free mint on my follow-up collection.
